<item>
            <title>[LU-9613] fix lock intent of cdt_llog_process in mdt_hsm_pending_restore</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9613</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For some reason the lock intent of &lt;tt&gt;cdt_llog_process()&lt;/tt&gt; was changed from &lt;tt&gt;WRITE&lt;/tt&gt; to &lt;tt&gt;READ&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;mdt_hsm_pending_restore()&lt;/tt&gt; without &lt;tt&gt;hsm_restore_cb()&lt;/tt&gt; being modified.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The lock intent should have remained WRITE.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
